 * comment node.

variables.name: PSEUDONAME_ANY
variables.comment: * Psuedo name for a wild card pattern ('*').

variables.name: PSEUDONAME_ROOT
variables.comment: * Psuedo name for the root node.

variables.name: PSEUDONAME_TEXT
variables.comment: * Psuedo name for a text node.

variables.name: PSEUDONAME_COMMENT
variables.comment: * Psuedo name for a comment node.

variables.name: PSEUDONAME_PI
variables.comment: * Psuedo name for a processing instruction node.

variables.name: PSEUDONAME_OTHER
variables.comment: * Psuedo name for an unknown type value.
